{
  "stem": "17135.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So-- in-- in a very, very beautiful home we had there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then we were playing soccer.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And-- and-- belonged-- we belonged, also, to a Jewish sports club, the Hakoah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We didn't-- there was-- there were two competing sports club-- Maccabi and Hakoah.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh my god.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't remember.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Soccer balls.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, did you have more than one?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 69,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 70,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, no, no, no, no, no, no, no.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I-- I did most of the fighting.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because my brother, the oldest brother, wanted to be the boss all the time.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't accept that.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I said, wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There is no birth right that you have [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so there were arguments going on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "You know.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "But-- but in-- in general, we stuck together, let's put it this way.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 71,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Obviously.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He was the peacemaker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He was the peacemaker.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "The second brother was always the peacemaker.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And if something was going on, I remember his-- he was such an altruist, that's the word.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "When-- when we did something wrong, and my parent want to know who did it, when something was broken, he volunteered always.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He volunteered.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "He was such an idealist.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And all his life, he was an idealist.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 72,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "That's probably the reason that he got in trouble, and-- and-- and didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I-- I-- interesting enough, she complains even now.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was her boss.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Everybody had a boss.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I commandeered her around.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because I was the older brother.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The two oldest brothers were very close.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And-- and-- and then-- there are always cliques when you have a lot of children.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 73,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was close to my sister.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So I-- I helped her.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I went to high school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "She went to high school.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "To do gymnasium.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 74,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She went to lyceum.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
